title: The Wicker Tree (2011)
description:
THE WICKER TREE (2011)
Directed and written by Robin Hardy

A companion to the classic The Wicker Man (1973), but not a sequel -- not "the continuing adventures of Lord Summerisle."

The difference between the two films can be adequately summed up in the observation that Anthony Shaffer wrote The Wicker Man, and Robin Hardy wrote the screenplay for The Wicker Tree as an adaptation of his novel (of the same title).

This is from an American DVD (NTSC) and includes the full-length feature film, the theatrical trailer and a 12 minute "Making of the Wicker Tree" promo (because they thought you'd like to know).
